item.title: Write 1 - a few favourite quotes
item.description: A few of my favourite quotes The moments that define lives aren’t always obvious. They don’t scream LEDGE, and nine times out of ten there’s no rope to duck under, no line to cross, no blood pact, no official letter on fancy paper.
